WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.001 --> 00:00:02.000
大家 好！
dà jiā hǎo
Hello, everybody!

2
00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.000
我 叫 江山，
wǒ jiào jiāng shān
My name is John

3
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.240
一个 会 说 汉语 的 美国人。
yí gè huì shuō hàn yǔ de měi guó rén
An American who can speak Chinese.

4
00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:17.920
请 跟 我 学学 汉语的 你好 和 英语的 hello 有 什么 不 一样。
qǐng gēn wǒ xué xué hàn yǔ de nǐ hǎo hé yīng yǔ de hello yǒu shén me bù yī yàng
You are going to learn the difference between "nihao" and "hello" from me.

5
00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:23.000
今天 我 要 去 君悦 酒店 开会，
jīn tiān wǒ yào  qù jūn yuè jiǔ diàn kāi huì
Today, I am going to attend a conference at the Grand Hyatt hotel.

6
00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:26.000
可是，我 迷路 了。
kě shì, wǒ mí lù le
But I got lost.

7
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
你好，请问 君悦 酒店 怎么 走。
nǐ hǎo qǐng wèn jūn yuè jiǔ diàn zěn me zǒu
Hello! Could you tell me how to get to the Grant Hyatt Hotel?

8
00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:36.000
往 那儿 走。
wǎng nà r zǒu
Go that way.

9
00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:39.880
谢谢，谢谢。
xiè xiè xiè xiè
Thanks a lot!

10
00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:01.000
你好 吗？
nǐ hǎo ma
"how do you do"

11
00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:02.040
妈，你好！
Mā, nǐ hǎo
“Hello, mom.”

12
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.000
好你妈！
hǎo nǐ ma
“fuck your mom!”

13
00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:16.920
江山，你 来 了
jiāng shān, nǐ lái le
Hey, John, you are here!

14
00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:20.600
李易，是 你，我 来 了
lǐ yì, shì nǐ, wǒ lái le
Hey Li Yi, yeah, I'm here.

15
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.000
做 什么 呢？
zuò shén me ne
What are you doing?

16
00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:24.000
没 什么
méi shén me
Nothing.

17
00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:27.000
我 给 你 介绍 一个 朋友 吧
wǒ gěi nǐ jiè shào yí gè péng yǒu ba
Let me introduce a friend to you!

18
00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:29.000
好啊
hǎo a
Great!

19
00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:30.720
跟 我 来
gēn wǒ lái
Follow me.

20
00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:37.080
老王！
lǎo wáng
Hey! Old Wang!

21
00:01:37.440 --> 00:01:38.920
小李！
xiǎo lǐ
Hey! Little Li!

22
00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:42.090
您好，
nín hǎo
Hello.

23
00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:43.040
我 姓 王，
wǒ xìng wáng
My surname is Wang.

24
00:01:43.100 --> 00:01:44.400
请问 您 贵姓？
Qǐngwèn nín guìxìng?
What is your honorable surname?

25
00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:46.000
您好，您好，
Nín hǎo, nín hǎo,
Hello, hello

26
00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:48.000
我 姓 江。
Wǒ xìng jiāng
